item.title: Illegal Cat Breeder @Rhodes
item.description: Last November, out of boredom and a desire to buy a Rocket Apartmento espresso machine, I booked a room in Rhodes. The guy who was renting the place at that time is an illegal cat breeder. I donâ€™t know if there are any laws for breeding cats, but anyway, he always had more than 10 cats, and it didn’t smell very pleasant. Cats aside, business wasn’t that bad, and I wanted to continue working occasionally, but the room was never available again.
